{"title":"The best photos from the UCI World Championships men’s road race 2024","link":"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/in-depth/world-championships-mens-road-race-gallery-2024","date":1727708911000,"content":"<p><a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk\">Cyclist</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/in-depth/world-championships-mens-road-race-gallery-2024\">The best photos from the UCI World Championships men’s road race 2024</a></p>\n\n<p>The men’s road race brought an end to the <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/tags/uci-world-championships\" target=\"_blank\">2024 UCI Road World Championships</a> over in Zürich, Switzerland on Sunday. The race for the men’s elite rainbow jersey was closely fought with Tadej Pogačar, <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/tags/mathieu-van-der-poel\" target=\"_blank\">Mathieu van der Poel</a> and <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/tags/remco-evenepoel\" target=\"_blank\">Remco Evenepoel</a> starting as favourites for the coveted prize.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>After attacking with a staggering 100km to go, <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/tags/tadej-pogacar\" target=\"_blank\">Tadej Pogačar</a> took the honours and a career-first rainbow jersey. In doing so, the Slovenian rounds out a successful Triple Crown attempt after winning the Giro d’Italia and Tour de France earlier this year. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>This morning in French newspaper <em>L’Équipe</em>, <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/in-depth/from-the-archive-in-conversation-with-eddy-merckx\" target=\"_blank\">Eddy Merckx</a> even admitted that Pogačar is above him’. The Slovenian disclosed after the race that it was ‘a silly move’, but it all paid off in the end. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Photographer Xavier Pereyron was on the scene to capture the action, memorialising just the third Triple Crown in men’s cycling history.</p>\n\n\n\n\n<div>\n<figure><div><img /></div><img width=\"647\" height=\"970\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0016-647x970.jpg\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0016-647x970.jpg 647w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0016-200x300.jpg 200w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0016-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0016-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0016-1365x2048.jpg 1365w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0016-750x1125.jpg 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0016-1140x1710.jpg 1140w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0016-scaled.jpg 1707w\" /><figcaption>Xavier Pereyron</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n<p>He means business.</p>\n\n\n<div>\n<figure><div><img /></div><img width=\"647\" height=\"970\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0007-min-647x970.jpg\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0007-min-647x970.jpg 647w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0007-min-200x300.jpg 200w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0007-min-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0007-min-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0007-min-1365x2048.jpg 1365w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0007-min-750x1125.jpg 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0007-min-1140x1710.jpg 1140w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0007-min-scaled.jpg 1707w\" /><figcaption>Xavier Pereyron</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n<p>I believe Gen Z describe this as ‘aura’.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><div><img /></div><img width=\"970\" height=\"647\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0002-970x647.jpg\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0002-970x646.jpg 970w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0002-300x200.jpg 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0002-768x512.jpg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0002-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0002-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0002-750x500.jpg 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0002-1140x760.jpg 1140w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0002-465x310.jpg 465w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0002-620x413.jpg 620w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0002-350x233.jpg 350w\" /><figcaption>Xavier Pereyron</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AeUonD5Xr_s\" target=\"_blank\">…Küng, Küng, Stefan Küng, Küng, Stefan, Stefan Küng, Küng…</a></p>\n\n\n\n<figure><div><img /></div><img width=\"970\" height=\"647\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0006-min-970x647.jpg\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0006-min-970x646.jpg 970w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0006-min-300x200.jpg 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0006-min-768x512.jpg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0006-min-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0006-min-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0006-min-750x500.jpg 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0006-min-1140x760.jpg 1140w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0006-min-465x310.jpg 465w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0006-min-620x413.jpg 620w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0006-min-350x233.jpg 350w\" /><figcaption>Xavier Pereyron</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Brits abroad.</p>\n\n\n<div>\n<figure><div><img /></div><img width=\"647\" height=\"970\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0014-min-647x970.jpg\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0014-min-647x970.jpg 647w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0014-min-200x300.jpg 200w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0014-min-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0014-min-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0014-min-1365x2048.jpg 1365w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0014-min-750x1125.jpg 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0014-min-1140x1710.jpg 1140w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0014-min-scaled.jpg 1707w\" /><figcaption>Xavier Pereyron</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n<p>‘Tim, when’s Remco going to attack?’</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><div><img /></div><img width=\"970\" height=\"647\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0037-970x647.jpg\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0037-970x646.jpg 970w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0037-300x200.jpg 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0037-768x512.jpg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0037-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0037-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0037-750x500.jpg 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0037-1140x760.jpg 1140w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0037-465x310.jpg 465w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0037-620x413.jpg 620w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0037-350x233.jpg 350w\" /><figcaption>Xavier Pereyron</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Let the games begin…</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><div><img /></div><img width=\"970\" height=\"647\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0031-970x647.jpg\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0031-970x646.jpg 970w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0031-300x200.jpg 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0031-768x512.jpg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0031-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0031-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0031-750x500.jpg 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0031-1140x760.jpg 1140w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0031-465x310.jpg 465w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0031-620x413.jpg 620w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0031-350x233.jpg 350w\" /><figcaption>Xavier Pereyron</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Understandably, Evenepoel was a marked man in Zürich. He was looking to seal an unprecedented ‘double-double’ after his <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/in-depth/mens-olympic-road-race-paris-2024-gallery\" target=\"_blank\">Olympic exploits</a> in August.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><div><img /></div><img width=\"970\" height=\"647\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0023-970x647.jpg\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0023-970x646.jpg 970w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0023-300x200.jpg 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0023-768x512.jpg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0023-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0023-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0023-750x500.jpg 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0023-1140x760.jpg 1140w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0023-465x310.jpg 465w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0023-620x413.jpg 620w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0023-350x233.jpg 350w\" /><figcaption>Xavier Pereyron</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>This is definitely Switzerland.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><div><img /></div><img width=\"970\" height=\"647\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0041-min-970x647.jpg\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0041-min-970x646.jpg 970w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0041-min-300x200.jpg 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0041-min-768x512.jpg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0041-min-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0041-min-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0041-min-750x500.jpg 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0041-min-1140x760.jpg 1140w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0041-min-465x310.jpg 465w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0041-min-620x413.jpg 620w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0041-min-350x233.jpg 350w\" /><figcaption>Xavier Pereyron</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Domen Novak sets the tone in the Slovenia-led peloton.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><div><img /></div><img width=\"970\" height=\"647\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0053-970x647.jpg\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0053-970x646.jpg 970w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0053-300x200.jpg 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0053-768x512.jpg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0053-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0053-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0053-750x500.jpg 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0053-1140x760.jpg 1140w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0053-465x310.jpg 465w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0053-620x413.jpg 620w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0053-350x233.jpg 350w\" /><figcaption>Xavier Pereyron</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The weather was much better than for the women, who had to fight against driving rain the day prior.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><div><img /></div><img width=\"970\" height=\"647\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0059-min-970x647.jpg\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0059-min-970x646.jpg 970w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0059-min-300x200.jpg 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0059-min-768x512.jpg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0059-min-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0059-min-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0059-min-750x500.jpg 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0059-min-1140x760.jpg 1140w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0059-min-465x310.jpg 465w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0059-min-620x413.jpg 620w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0059-min-350x233.jpg 350w\" /><figcaption>Xavier Pereyron</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>At the 100km to go marker, Tadej Pogačar was already off the front. He soon caught the escape group and attacked with French trade teammate Pavel Sivakov.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><div><img /></div><img width=\"970\" height=\"647\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0064-min-970x647.jpg\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0064-min-970x646.jpg 970w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0064-min-300x200.jpg 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0064-min-768x512.jpg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0064-min-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0064-min-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0064-min-750x500.jpg 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0064-min-1140x760.jpg 1140w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0064-min-465x310.jpg 465w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0064-min-620x413.jpg 620w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0064-min-350x233.jpg 350w\" /><figcaption>Xavier Pereyron</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Behind, the chase was on. Mathieu van der Poel was among the riders holding back.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><div><img /></div><img width=\"970\" height=\"647\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0060-min-970x647.jpg\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0060-min-970x646.jpg 970w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0060-min-300x200.jpg 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0060-min-768x512.jpg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0060-min-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0060-min-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0060-min-750x500.jpg 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0060-min-1140x760.jpg 1140w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0060-min-465x310.jpg 465w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0060-min-620x413.jpg 620w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0060-min-350x233.jpg 350w\" /><figcaption>Xavier Pereyron</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>After working with Sivakov initially, Pogačar set off on his own with 52km remaining in the race.</p>\n\n\n<div>\n<figure><div><img /></div><img width=\"647\" height=\"970\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0068-647x970.jpg\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0068-647x970.jpg 647w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0068-200x300.jpg 200w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0068-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0068-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0068-1365x2048.jpg 1365w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0068-750x1125.jpg 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0068-1140x1710.jpg 1140w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0068-scaled.jpg 1707w\" /><figcaption>Xavier Pereyron</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n<p>‘Let me check what Twitter’s saying about this Pogačar attack’.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><div><img /></div><img width=\"970\" height=\"647\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0069-min-970x647.jpg\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0069-min-970x646.jpg 970w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0069-min-300x200.jpg 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0069-min-768x512.jpg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0069-min-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0069-min-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0069-min-750x500.jpg 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0069-min-1140x760.jpg 1140w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0069-min-465x310.jpg 465w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0069-min-620x413.jpg 620w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0069-min-350x233.jpg 350w\" /><figcaption>Xavier Pereyron</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The crowds help to ooze out a couple of extra watts over the climb.</p>\n\n\n<div>\n<figure><div><img /></div><img width=\"647\" height=\"970\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0083-min-647x970.jpg\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0083-min-647x970.jpg 647w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0083-min-200x300.jpg 200w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0083-min-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0083-min-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0083-min-1365x2048.jpg 1365w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0083-min-750x1125.jpg 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0083-min-1140x1710.jpg 1140w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0083-min-scaled.jpg 1707w\" /><figcaption>Xavier Pereyron</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n<p>The dictionary definition of strength on the bike.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><div><img /></div><img width=\"970\" height=\"647\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0077-min-970x647.jpg\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0077-min-970x646.jpg 970w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0077-min-300x200.jpg 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0077-min-768x512.jpg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0077-min-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0077-min-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0077-min-750x500.jpg 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0077-min-1140x760.jpg 1140w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0077-min-465x310.jpg 465w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0077-min-620x413.jpg 620w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0077-min-350x233.jpg 350w\" /><figcaption>Xavier Pereyron</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The gap to the lone leader Pogačar ebbed and flowed during the final lap.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><div><img /></div><img width=\"970\" height=\"647\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0066-min-970x647.jpg\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0066-min-970x646.jpg 970w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0066-min-300x200.jpg 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0066-min-768x512.jpg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0066-min-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0066-min-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0066-min-750x500.jpg 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0066-min-1140x760.jpg 1140w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0066-min-465x310.jpg 465w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0066-min-620x413.jpg 620w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0066-min-350x233.jpg 350w\" /><figcaption>Xavier Pereyron</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Behind, the race was fracturing over the steep kickers.</p>\n\n\n<div>\n<figure><div><img /></div><img width=\"647\" height=\"970\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0076-647x970.jpg\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0076-647x970.jpg 647w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0076-200x300.jpg 200w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0076-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0076-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0076-1365x2048.jpg 1365w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0076-750x1125.jpg 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0076-1140x1710.jpg 1140w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0076-scaled.jpg 1707w\" /><figcaption>Xavier Pereyron</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n<p>Tufts out, Pogačar continued his charge for the Worlds title and the rainbow jersey.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><div><img /></div><img width=\"970\" height=\"647\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0089-min-970x647.jpg\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0089-min-970x646.jpg 970w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0089-min-300x200.jpg 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0089-min-768x512.jpg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0089-min-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0089-min-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0089-min-750x500.jpg 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0089-min-1140x760.jpg 1140w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0089-min-465x310.jpg 465w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0089-min-620x413.jpg 620w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0089-min-350x233.jpg 350w\" /><figcaption>Xavier Pereyron</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The gold might have weighed Remco down.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><div><img /></div><img width=\"970\" height=\"647\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0094-min-970x647.jpg\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0094-min-970x646.jpg 970w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0094-min-300x200.jpg 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0094-min-768x512.jpg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0094-min-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0094-min-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0094-min-750x500.jpg 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0094-min-1140x760.jpg 1140w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0094-min-465x310.jpg 465w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0094-min-620x413.jpg 620w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0094-min-350x233.jpg 350w\" /><figcaption>Xavier Pereyron</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Toms Skujiņš and Ben Healy chased, but their efforts were soon brought back by the main group of favourites. They’d end up battling it out for the remaining medals.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><div><img /></div><img width=\"970\" height=\"647\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0105-min-970x647.jpg\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0105-min-970x646.jpg 970w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0105-min-300x200.jpg 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0105-min-768x512.jpg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0105-min-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0105-min-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0105-min-750x500.jpg 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0105-min-1140x760.jpg 1140w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0105-min-465x310.jpg 465w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0105-min-620x413.jpg 620w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0105-min-350x233.jpg 350w\" /><figcaption>Xavier Pereyron</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The money shot. The Triple Crown is in the bag.</p>\n\n\n<div>\n<figure><div><img /></div><img width=\"776\" height=\"970\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0109-min-776x970.jpg\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-S