g99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0111-min-750x500.jpg 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0111-min-1140x760.jpg 1140w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0111-min-465x310.jpg 465w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0111-min-620x413.jpg 620w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0111-min-350x233.jpg 350w\" /><figcaption>Xavier Pereyron</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>A well-deserved cooldown.</p>\n\n\n<div>\n<figure><img width=\"647\" height=\"970\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0115-min-647x970.jpg\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0115-min-647x970.jpg 647w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0115-min-200x300.jpg 200w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0115-min-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0115-min-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0115-min-1365x2048.jpg 1365w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0115-min-750x1125.jpg 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0115-min-1140x1710.jpg 1140w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0115-min-scaled.jpg 1707w\" /><figcaption>Xavier Pereyron</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n<p>The stars aligned for Pogačar in 2024, well and truly.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><div><img /></div><img width=\"970\" height=\"606\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0117-min-970x606.jpg\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0117-min-970x606.jpg 970w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0117-min-300x188.jpg 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0117-min-768x480.jpg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0117-min-1536x960.jpg 1536w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0117-min-2048x1280.jpg 2048w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0117-min-750x469.jpg 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0117-min-1140x713.jpg 1140w\" /><figcaption>Xavier Pereyron</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Between these two, they have won two world titles and twelve Monuments. Sorry Wout, but these guys are the best one-day racers around.</p>\n\n\n<div>\n<figure><div><img /></div><img width=\"647\" height=\"970\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0130-min-647x970.jpg\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0130-min-647x970.jpg 647w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0130-min-200x300.jpg 200w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0130-min-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0130-min-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0130-min-1365x2048.jpg 1365w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0130-min-750x1125.jpg 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0130-min-1140x1710.jpg 1140w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/09/Worlds-Cyclist-Sunday-Race-29092024-0130-min-scaled.jpg 1707w\" /><figcaption>Xavier Pereyron</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n<p>I think we’re going to get very familiar with rainbow Tadej.</p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/in-depth/world-championships-mens-road-race-gallery-2024\">The best photos from the UCI World Championships men’s road race 2024</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk\">Cyclist</a>.</p>","author":"Ewan Wilson &#124; Staff Writer","siteTitle":"Cyclist.co.uk","siteHash":"561486e7070fa5351de9318ad0fa26c2a39332acba5fc7c7d1694a01d53d431e","entryHash":"f11392e58a498c94902abaf0a94458e675183c6df7c1bdab398cdc981b51479d","category":"Cycling"}